# Cursor Rules for XiDeAI Pro

- Always prefer English for code and Turkish for user-facing text.
- Follow the Service/OperationManager pattern for all new features.
- When modifying Windows Forms, ensure thread safety with `InvokeIfRequired` or `BeginInvoke`.
- Use the existing `Logger` class for all diagnostics.
- Refer to `.agent/rules/core_logic.md` for project-wide standards.
